        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Mumbai/scene_mongoose.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 22cdb031-155a-441f-a882-336dfc7b04e1).Image",
        "Description": "Sidemen have fallen apart after a private group chat was leaked, triggering public outrage and serious criminal charges. With authorities closing in, part of the group vanished overseas. Now hiding in the chaos of Mumbai, they have adopted new identities and blended into the city’s sprawl. KSI operates under the name Kafe, Vik has reinvented himself as Eklavya, Simon answers to Abhay, and Josh now goes by Manish. Separated from their former lives but still connected by loyalty and secrecy.",
